                Title: "How Could We Organize In The Furry Fandom?",
                SubTitle: "",
                Abstract:
                    "Current events are stressful, and we could all use a\r\nbreak. But what constructive things could the furry fandom offer us in such trying times?\r\nIn this newly updated and illustrated talk, we explore what makes furry special, what we\r\ncan currently do to make a difference in today's world, and what exciting and hopeful\r\nfutures we may build thanks to the best parts of the fandom.",
