                Title: "Furry Tails Theater",
                SubTitle: "Seating",
                Abstract:
                    "Live performance theater? Fursuits? Song and dance? You can find it all (except the\r\nsinging) at the main stage! \"Fish 'n' Ships\" will take you to the legendary Food Wars of\r\nTortuga, where a lifelong feud between two cooks reaches its boiling point…",
