                ConferenceRoomId: "979f4ecf-66bd-4c83-ac3c-c3636ff82a81",
                Description:
                    "Have you ever wondered what our world would look like if piracy had never been outlawed? How\r\nwould we live and act in a universe where the \"Arr!\" never became part of \"Atrocious\"?\r\nThink no more! Instead, come and experience what we've set in scene for you. Join us on\r\na wild ride and follow the epic battle of the chefs in the Furry Drama Company production:\r\n\"Fish 'n' Ships\".\r\n\r\nFor the first time at Eurofurence, we're showing a full theater piece on the main stage,\r\ncomplete with cute fursuits, fiery choreographies, brilliant humor, and of course, a food\r\nwar, conducted with weapons of wit, whey and Worcestershire sauce.\r\n\r\nFish 'n' Ships is a live performed theatre production and has been prepared by the Furry\r\nDrama Company, a team of live performance enthusiasts directed by Tsuki and Martini.",
