                    "**Tables will be torn down at this time. Artists and dealers must have cleared their tables beforehand!**\r\n\r\nYou're an artist, but didn't get a table at the Dealers' Den or simply decided that it is not for you? Then the Artist Alley might be just the right place for you! No application necessary — just grab a table: \"First come, first served.\" Whenever there's an empty table, feel free to sit down and offer your services with sketches, badges, prints and a smile.\r\n\r\n**Once you're done** doing business or feel like you've got enough commissions to fill some time, **please free up your table**, as another artist might be interested in having a go as well. Please also make sure to check bulletins for updated information.  If you download the Eurofurence smartphone app, you can publish \"come find me\" announcements on our Telegram and Dealers' Den Twitter channels. There's only one downside: due to German law, **selling adult material in public areas is strictly forbidden**.",
