                ConferenceRoomId: "8e9a2236-c83b-4206-aff8-fe73880e796a",
                Description:
                    "Open space workshop for everyone interested in trying out some ponyplay related stuff and gear. \r\n\r\nThe workshop itself will consist of two parts. The first (and quite short) part will be a theoretical introduction to ponyplay. The goal is to give everyone attending an idea about the diversity of playstyles and possibilities when doing ponyplay and to get everyone warmed up a bit. \r\n\r\nAfter that you will have the opportunity to try out different things yourself like pony dressage or trying out some pony gear you've always have been curious about. There will hopefully be plenty of time and opportunity for that. I'm not sure yet if I will be able to provide for cart pulling as well, due to the venue having less space available, but we'll try to make it available if we can.\r\n\r\nConsider the whole atmosphere to be very open, friendly and casual.\r\n\r\nPlease don't dress up without prior approval – only the panelists will have the opportunity to do so. Security will make sure that no kink gear is worn outside of the panel room. For more information about being a panelist please contact @raymondfeesh.",
