                ConferenceRoomId: "3465b19a-fe53-45fd-b3ee-e6df1be71e15",
                Description:
                    "In the Dealers' Den artists and dealers from all over the world sell all kinds of furry-related art, prints, sketches, books, comics, t-shirts and all different kinds of merchandise for your daily furry life. They also offer various other goods like fursuit partials, fursuit accessories, home-made treats, jewelry or they may have scoured the Seven Seas for great books and comics to bring to Eurofurence. Meet your favorite artist or just roam around and gather some inspiration from everything on display here.\r\n\r\nPlease note that some artists offer theme-related or Eurofurence-exclusive goods that you may not be able to obtain anywhere else. At our Eurofurence Shop you can get old EF shirts and other leftover goodies. Missed a design? Ask what sizes are still in stock.\r\n\r\n*Sponsors and Supersponsors only – general admittance after 14:00!*",
