                ConferenceRoomId: "62060c43-76a8-49de-8389-511790f52917",
                Description:
                    "Fox Amoore and Pepper Coyote host a panel on the wonderful world of musical production. From aspiring hobbyists to professionals, come and join a conversation highlighting some of the latest in music technology, instruments and software that is available to us today.\r\n\r\nWe will cover several aspects of music including production and sequencing (Are you a Cubase nerd or a Protools... Pro?), first steps into learning an instrument, virtual instruments and their applications in recording, mixing and mastering, and even going about getting your music released onto physical media such as records, CDs and cassettes.\r\n\r\nCome join to listen, share your insights and experiences... and let's all leave having taught something new to one another.",
