                DisplayName: "Oktavia's Creatures",
                Merchandise: "Fursuits, Sewing templates, Fursuit props and accessories",
                ShortDescription: "Premade fursuit partial, Sewing templates, Fursuit collars with cute tags and Fursuiting essentials!",
                AboutTheArtistText:
                    "Hello there!\r\nThe name is Unity, I'm a 26 year old Danish fursuit maker!\r\nI've been making fursuits since 2013 that started out by a simple YouTube video back in 2011.\r\nBut after years of carving foam, inhaling airbrushing fumes, hot glue burns and being chronically covered in fur from top to toe I've made my fursuit making business my full time job in 2018.\r\n\r\nBesides fursuit making I make: Collars, Bandanas, fursuit props, Fursuit essentials and my own sewing templates!",
                AboutTheArtText:
                    "-Sewing template-\r\nYou wanna master making unique hand paws? \r\nThen come check out my homemade sewing templates! I offer a few different kinds:\r\n-Feral style hand paws (both feline and canine)\r\n-4 fingered poofy paws\r\n-Sergal/dragon style paws\r\n-5 fingered poofy paws\r\nAll of them will have finished examples presented so you can touch and visualize how your very own project will look like. \r\n\r\n-Premade fursuit partial-\r\nThis year I'll be brining a brand new and never used brown hyena fursuit!\r\n\r\n-Fursuit accessories-\r\nI love making fursuit sized collars with colorful printed fabric. They also come with cute resin printed tags that has been hand painted.\r\n\r\n-Fursuiting essentials- \r\nHomemade balaclavas made with beautiful printed jersey fabrics.",
